# ============================================================
# [*adopt-repo] COMMAND (NEW - 2026-03-21):
#   0. MANDATORY: Load external-repo-adoption-checklist (95 items)
#   1. PHASE 1: Copy ALL squads (agents, tasks, workflows, checklists)
#   2. PHASE 2: Copy ALL .aiox-core enhancements (AI, monitor, scripts)
#   3. PHASE 3: Copy ALL tools & infrastructure (MCP, scripts, patches)
#   4. PHASE 4: Copy ALL IDE integrations (.claude, .cursor, .gemini)
#   5. PHASE 5: Copy ALL configuration (env, squad-lock, CLAUDE.md, rules)
#   6. PHASE 6: Copy ALL documentation (docs, case studies, reference)
#   7. PHASE 7: Copy ALL governance rules (agent-authority, workflows)
#   8. PHASE 8: Run 95-point verification checklist - ALL MUST PASS
#   9. PHASE 9: Create comprehensive adoption documents + commit
#   10. CRITICAL: Do not mark COMPLETE until ALL 95 checks verified
#   11. USER RULE: No "tem mais alguma coisa" - exhaustive by design
# ============================================================
COMMANDS_RULE_ADOPT_REPO_0=Load external-repo-adoption-checklist with 95 verification points
COMMANDS_RULE_ADOPT_REPO_1=Copy all squads: agents + tasks + workflows + checklists
COMMANDS_RULE_ADOPT_REPO_2=Copy all .aiox-core: workflow-intelligence + monitor + scripts + schemas
COMMANDS_RULE_ADOPT_REPO_3=Copy all tools: MCP servers + automation + infrastructure
COMMANDS_RULE_ADOPT_REPO_4=Copy all IDE integrations: .claude .cursor .gemini .codex .antigravity
COMMANDS_RULE_ADOPT_REPO_5=Copy all configuration: .env .squad-lock core-config CLAUDE.md
COMMANDS_RULE_ADOPT_REPO_6=Copy all documentation: docs case-studies README runbooks
COMMANDS_RULE_ADOPT_REPO_7=Copy all governance: agent-authority workflow-execution rules
COMMANDS_RULE_ADOPT_REPO_8=Verify all 95 checklist items BEFORE marking complete
COMMANDS_RULE_ADOPT_REPO_9=Create adoption analysis + completion document
COMMANDS_RULE_ADOPT_REPO_10=Commit each phase with comprehensive commit messages
COMMANDS_RULE_ADOPT_REPO_11=Final status: ZERO items left behind - GUARANTEED
COMMANDS_RULE_ADOPT_REPO_12=If user asks "tem mais alguma coisa" - failure (checklist wasn't thorough)

